item_name: Giovanna Signature Women's 2-pc Polka Dot Brocade Suit
product_description: You'll never go wrong with this classic looking suit from Giovanna Signature. Featuring notched collar, polka-dot pattern in black and white brocade, complimentary modesty panel, trimmed with black lace, bell cuffs, 3 rhinestone button jacket closure, fishtail style skirt sweep… all these details make this suit a gorgeous garment to keep in your wardrobe! Hat on model is sold separately. Measurements taken from size 10: jacket length 24" - 25", skirt length 31".
